Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.97,0:01:03.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He came to visit me sometimes...until recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.26,0:01:06.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Long time no see, Kida Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.17,0:01:09.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.84,0:01:13.66,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,They disappeared after an altercation with another gang.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.66,0:01:17.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And you can't just go ask Orihara Izaya, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.17,0:01:20.05,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,You dragged me back into this...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:20.98,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.43,0:01:22.22,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.85,0:01:55.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your friend was hospitalized?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.74,0:01:57.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who'd you hear that from?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.92,0:01:59.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw it from my window.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.75,0:02:01.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You came to visit every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.05,0:02:04.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, your friend's a girl, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.51,0:02:09.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She has a nice body and wears glasses; that lack \Nof balance makes her an attractive high schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.87,0:02:10.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like her?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.90,0:02:15.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I'm smack dab in the middle of \Na love triangle involving her and my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.02,0:02:17.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be a love square if you included me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.59,0:02:23.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done, finished, canceled, closed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.81,0:02:25.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.00,0:02:27.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then why do you keep visiting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.30,0:02:30.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you decided you want to return to how things were?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.79,0:02:33.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.24,0:02:36.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll come back, Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.34,0:02:39.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you always do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.54,0:02:43.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm fine no matter how many girls you fall in love with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:49.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, you'll show a much stronger\N love toward me than any of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.49,0:02:52.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't have to listen to know what she was going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.19,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,She always repeats the same thing;
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.64,0:02:58.94,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,that I'll return to her no matter how many girls I date.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:06.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And, more so than any of them, you'll love me on a much higher level.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.06,0:03:09.71,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,However, I didn't want to hear the words that would come next.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.71,0:03:13.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, that's what Izaya said.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.74,0:03:22.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I succumb to the illusion that I'm God when I look \Nat it like this, which feels pretty good, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.91,0:03:25.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Three-way fights are great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:27.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, all three leaders are friends with each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.99,0:03:30.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,God attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:40.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The sweeter the honeymoon, the higher the flames\N of despair rise when it all comes crashing down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:45.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Look! The pawns are like garbage!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.02,0:03:51.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, what do the cards say about the non-pawns?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.60,0:03:54.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadota's group, Shinra, Simon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm...I guess Shizu-chan's the king after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.69,0:04:02.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Celty's the queen, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.60,0:04:04.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then who's the joker...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.01,0:04:08.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Meh, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.26,0:04:12.35,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This has gotten fun, hasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.84,0:04:15.65,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.56,0:04:28.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that she didn't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.08,0:04:31.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How fortunate.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.99,0:04:33.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll all work out as long as she's alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.08,0:04:35.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.50,0:04:37.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty smart;
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.77,0:04:42.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you understand that you're the reason she ended up like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.55,0:04:47.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's laudable that you haven't succumbed \Nto your emotions and tried to punch me—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.51,0:04:52.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Bingo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:55.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's only natural that you'd channel your anger towards me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.79,0:04:58.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since I was obviously trying to insult you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.67,0:05:01.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, she's unconscious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.21,0:05:02.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope she wakes up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.78,0:05:07.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Or maybe you hope that she'll never come out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.34,0:05:10.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to say...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.56,0:05:12.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know....
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.22,0:05:13.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're scared, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.78,0:05:17.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You figure that if she wakes up,\N she'll blame you for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.17,0:05:22.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, let's assume that she dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.01,0:05:27.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you feel guilty for the rest of your life that you killed her?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:32.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, your feelings of guilt are\N meaningless whether she lives or dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.20,0:05:34.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:38.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The past will be only too happy to chase you—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.56,0:05:42.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In absolute, complete, and total earnest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.34,0:05:44.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you know why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.37,0:05:46.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.29,0:05:50.21,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The past and memories get lonely easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.21,0:05:53.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe in God.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.40,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because he doesn't have a fixed form.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.11,0:06:01.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The past certainly does exist, even in a world \Nwhere the future doesn't have a fixed form.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.42,0:06:05.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's been colored by misunderstandings and delusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.36,0:06:10.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,a person's past can't be anything but \Nthe truth as long as he believes in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's what you base your actions...or your way of life on,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.30,0:06:18.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,isn't that like being a deity?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.24,0:06:21.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand what you're trying to say at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.90,0:06:23.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you do...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.77,0:06:26.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run from her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.23,0:06:30.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings of guilt towards her will become \Nyour past, and she'll become a deity to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.46,0:06:33.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, that should be fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.52,0:06:36.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Since you like her...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.85,0:06:43.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see you've recovered wonderfully, Anri!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:46.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's great; Anri and her eros are safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.00,0:06:47.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Eros" is going too far, Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.27,0:06:51.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm really glad you're okay. I really am.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.30,0:06:54.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, umm...thanks, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.04,0:06:56.26,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.26,0:07:00.02,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy as long as you and your eros are okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The same for me—except for the eros thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.05,0:07:05.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.69,0:07:06.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.75,0:07:07.61,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:09.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.60,0:07:12.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry! Something just came up with my friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.36,0:07:14.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.05,0:07:17.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to hate someone, hate my friend to your heart's content!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.42,0:07:20.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hate doesn't cost anything, and it doesn't cause me any harm!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.73,0:07:24.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a perfect "two birds with one \Nstone," it's "many wives for one man!"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.48,0:07:25.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"Many wives for one man?"
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.49,0:07:28.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.62,0:07:31.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's really that important?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.90,0:07:36.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you think Kida's been acting strange lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.00,0:07:37.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.59,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure it's not all in your head?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.70,0:07:44.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never told Mikado about my \Ninvolvement in the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.65,0:07:49.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Where he is and this place are both realities to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:52.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But I feel like an incredible distance separates them...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:56.72,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We fought every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.72,0:08:00.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd stay connected to each other only if we continued to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:03.71,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted someone to affirm my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.71,0:08:07.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It was then...that I first met Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.54,0:08:09.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That yellow cloth looks really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.25,0:08:11.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.34,0:08:16.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're much cooler than the rumors make you out to be, Kida Masaomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.60,0:08:17.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.63,0:08:19.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How do you know my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.49,0:08:20.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have ESP?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.57,0:08:22.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Itou the ESP user?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.25,0:08:27.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really can read people's minds like that, I'm going \Nto put you in my bag and take you home with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.06,0:08:30.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you... That's just too weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:34.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But, it's not me. Someone else has ESP.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.88,0:08:36.41,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Eh? Who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:38.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a girl with ESP here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.63,0:08:40.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, he's an amazing person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:43.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.30,0:08:47.18,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It was also the time...I met someone I didn't want to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.18,0:08:52.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, nice to meet you. You're Kida Masaomi, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.66,0:08:53.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And who might you be?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:57.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Orihara Izaya, an information dealer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.23,0:09:00.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This girl's something like my disciple.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.89,0:09:03.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not her boyfriend or anything, so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.76,0:09:04.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope we get along.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.39,0:09:12.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shogun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.40,0:09:16.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to just call me Kida Masaomi, not "shogun."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.96,0:09:20.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But, "Kida" still sounds kind of...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:23.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know anything about the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.10,0:09:28.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We have some members who used to be a part \Nof them, but no one knows who's at the top.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.34,0:09:32.89,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They couldn't identify who it was during \Ntheir first gathering six months ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.89,0:09:35.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are they planning on making a move?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.22,0:09:39.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently their leader issued a statement \Nsaying he wanted information on the Slasher.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.72,0:09:42.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I guess it wasn't true that the Slasher is part of the Dollars.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.80,0:09:46.16,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even so, something about this is definitely fishy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.34,0:09:48.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.14,0:09:51.88,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Horada got attacked by the black biker, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:53.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Horada?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.04,0:10:01.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It was a while ago, but the black biker attacked us while we \Nwere making fun of some weird guy for wearing a white gas mask...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.39,0:10:02.70,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The black biker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.70,0:10:08.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was covered with something \Nthat looked like black oil or whatnot...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.36,0:10:11.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just who is this black biker...?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.43,0:10:13.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a rumor that it's involved with the Dollars...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.83,0:10:15.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.57,0:10:18.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you guys are older than us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.78,0:10:20.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.59,0:10:23.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't drag in any more adults.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:30.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're done for once we have people's names \Ngetting out like Mr. Whoever from Whatever Group.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.19,0:10:33.48,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're just little brats!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.48,0:10:39.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how many of us there are, we can't win \Nagainst adults, and we're done for if we get used by them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.60,0:10:44.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like...Orihara Izaya used me...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.40,0:10:48.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.57,0:10:49.04,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.04,0:10:55.05,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever I was even the least bit troubled, \NSaki would always say, "Just ask Izaya."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.37,0:10:58.42,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,We'd ask for his opinion on certain things.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.42,0:11:01.84,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I made it so that you both benefit...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.51,0:11:06.47,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone thought he was annoying at first, but\N things actually went well when we did what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.21,0:11:09.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.35,0:11:12.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I figured I wouldn't get any closer to him than need be.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:15.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya's really amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.34,0:11:18.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He knows everything and he's never wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.92,0:11:21.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, would you die if he told you to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.74,0:11:23.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:26.36,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I took pity on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.36,0:11:30.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to release her from Izaya's bonds.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:33.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if we can say that we're dating?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.67,0:11:35.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.60,0:11:39.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why do you hang out with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.40,0:11:41.83,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.77,0:11:46.63,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Did that Izaya guy tell you to like me or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.63,0:11:49.14,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. Only at first, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.60,0:11:52.81,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya doesn't interfere with people's love lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:55.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So, why do you still like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.27,0:11:57.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.06,0:12:00.11,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, maybe it's because you're cute?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.11,0:12:01.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:02.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.95,0:12:07.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I'd like you if you stopped your zealous devotion to that guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.15,0:12:08.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't help that.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.76,0:12:12.50,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if you'd overlook at least one of my faults.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.50,0:12:15.03,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know your own faults?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.03,0:12:16.18,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.18,0:12:17.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Although I don't plan on fixing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.54,0:12:19.47,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have a fault, you should fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.47,0:12:21.69,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll even help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.84,0:12:26.85,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, we started dating.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:33.26,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,When I was dating Saki, there was no one to keep me in check.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.26,0:12:38.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was serious, and the Yellow Scarves were even \Nmore serious when it came to fighting the Blue Squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.80,0:12:42.45,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They fought dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.45,0:12:46.53,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They'd attack small groups with large ones, \Nand they'd lay traps so they could win fights.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.02,0:12:49.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,They injured over one hundred of my compatriots.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.62,0:12:50.54,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone was scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.03,0:12:52.04,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so was I.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.04,0:12:55.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was scared that I'd have to disband the Yellow \NScarves and lose my sense of belonging.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.33,0:12:57.42,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.42,0:12:59.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should ask Izaya about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.48,0:13:02.63,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I relied on someone.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:05.93,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,On him...out of fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.21,0:13:07.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:10.65,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept telling myself it was for my friends' sakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.65,0:13:12.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take our time talking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.71,0:13:16.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,His information changed the Yellow Scarves drastically.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.35,0:13:18.26,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't just information about the Blue Squares...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.26,0:13:21.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He even gave us specific information on how to fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.52,0:13:25.32,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Our position as the weaker party was quickly reversed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:28.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izaya, you truly are amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.03,0:13:30.03,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,At some point, I'd lost my apprehension about him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.03,0:13:32.85,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, we were winning...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.85,0:13:34.58,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I enjoyed our victories.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.24,0:13:36.28,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.52,0:13:40.66,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kiiiiida Masaomi?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:41.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.67,0:13:43.31,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.31,0:13:46.57,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Izumii, the leader of the Blue Squares!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.57,0:13:48.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We're holding a trivia tournament today!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.76,0:13:53.62,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Question one: we've asked a special guest to join us; whoever could it be?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.62,0:13:58.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a hint; this person's very, very, very, very important to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.58,0:13:58.38,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.38,0:14:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Time's up! Or so I'd like to say, but an image \Nof someone flitted across your mind, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.54,0:14:08.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Then bingo, bingo, bingo, bingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.92,0:14:10.48,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,What have you... What have you done with Saki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.48,0:14:15.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Question two: What could your precious \Ngirlfriend possibly look like at this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.86,0:14:17.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Question three:
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.73,0:14:22.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was the sound of what bone breaking?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.94,0:14:27.15,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's a hint: I don't think she'll be walking any time soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:34.39,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Last question: If you don't come to the parking garage \Nwhere you trapped us last time within the next 20 minutes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.39,0:14:38.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,what in the world will become of this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.05,0:14:41.85,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I regretted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.85,0:14:43.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd been naïve.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.57,0:14:47.00,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter if I said, "We were still middle schoolers,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.00,0:14:49.28,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Or, "This is just the continuation of a backyard brawl,"
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.82,0:14:51.80,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.41,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This was war.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.93,0:14:58.16,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I was the one who started it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.16,0:14:59.51,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Pick up!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.51,0:15:01.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, pick up...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.19,0:15:08.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person you have dialed—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:10.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell?! Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.56,0:15:16.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Izumii, the girl passed out.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.59,0:15:18.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How boring.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.33,0:15:22.10,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just broke one of her bones in a couple of places...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.77,0:15:24.15,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I ran.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.15,0:15:25.90,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,All I could do was go there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:30.48,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd go there...and kill everyone who made Saki scream like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.21,0:15:35.95,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The person...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.95,0:15:41.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we're going to knock the \Nleader of the Yellow Scarves down a notch.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.29,0:15:43.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told you I'm not taking part in this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.12,0:15:45.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon now, I heard we kidnapped his girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.96,0:15:48.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's just a kid, but she's still pretty womanly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can have some fun with that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.31,0:15:52.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You kidnapped her?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.77,0:15:55.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, I'll head out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.00,0:15:57.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it! I knew this—
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.09,0:15:59.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell this to Izumii when you wake up:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.56,0:16:01.38,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,"So long, you bastard."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.89,0:16:15.37,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't move anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.66,0:16:18.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,What I'd felt earlier had just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.69,0:16:23.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did my feet freeze in place...even \Nthough I knew Saki was in danger?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:24.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I so scared?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.98,0:16:31.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought I could do anything if it were for Saki's sake...!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.07,0:16:34.76,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a powerless...middle schooler.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't she die at this rate?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:39.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Not like we care, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.06,0:16:41.77,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She's not bleeding, so she should be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.77,0:16:43.43,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.43,0:16:44.97,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, well—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.97,0:16:47.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa, so you really did kidnap her!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.09,0:16:50.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's just you, Yumasaki? Where's Kadota?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.64,0:16:56.93,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In reality, this girl would end up in \Npieces, unlike in the movies or manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.93,0:16:58.49,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That got me thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.49,0:16:59.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.37,0:17:04.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe that if a hero were to appear and save \Nher, just maybe the world would turn into 2D,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.12,0:17:08.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd become a superpower-wielding world savior,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:11.86,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and I'd be all over the girls like, "Oh my, \Ntee hee," and, "honk honk, heh heh heh."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.86,0:17:15.37,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, to realize my dream, here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.12,0:17:16.17,Secondary,,0000,0000,0000,,He's still as weird as ever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.45,0:17:24.05,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, it's time to implement my "let's turn reality \Ninto a happy ending for a 2D heroic story" plan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.76,0:17:38.78,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.19,0:17:44.25,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kadota, you asshole!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.83,0:17:49.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We probably shouldn't move her too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.36,0:17:51.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should get her to a hospital fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.76,0:17:53.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you two really okay with this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.11,0:17:58.72,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We follow you, Kadota, so we won't have any \Nlingering attachments to the Blue Squares.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.72,0:18:02.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, I'm not good at dealing \Nwith people like Izumii and Horada.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.19,0:18:05.60,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're always like, "I second that."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.27,0:18:13.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It would've been cooler if you'd thrown it out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.64,0:18:16.53,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like littering.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.10,0:18:25.31,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Saki finally woke up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.31,0:18:33.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to her testimony, Izumii was arrested, and \Nthe weakened Blue Squares were forced to disband.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.91,0:18:37.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.87,0:18:38.30,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.29,0:18:41.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Kida from the Yellow Scarves, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.34,0:18:43.94,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, who are you...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.51,0:18:46.80,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I explain...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.80,0:18:48.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My name's Kadota.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:53.73,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, I just heard that you betrayed your gang to save Saki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.73,0:18:56.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Um...thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.32,0:19:02.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we're on our way back from visiting her, \Nbut she said you haven't come to her room yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.75,0:19:05.40,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's none of your concern, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:07.59,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She asked us to tell you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.59,0:19:11.19,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She can see this whole area from her room.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.71,0:19:14.42,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She says, "Thanks for always coming to visit me."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.23,0:19:22.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I told her that you were held up by the \NBlue Squares and got there a little too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.08,0:19:27.45,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She wasn't mad at you or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.45,0:19:29.06,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.06,0:19:30.22,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.22,0:19:31.85,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did you tell her that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:34.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When did I ever tell you to do that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.30,0:19:39.27,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I would've told her the same thing even if you'd said not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:40.76,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You know, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.76,0:19:43.46,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That I...ran away...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.46,0:19:46.07,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My legs froze up...and I couldn't move...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.07,0:19:47.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.64,0:19:50.33,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, you're still running from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:54.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you telling me...to lie to her?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.23,0:19:56.71,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I abandoned her and ran away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.26,0:20:00.64,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, don't get carried away.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.64,0:20:02.87,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you remember the guilt you felt at running away,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.87,0:20:06.67,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,then at least bear the discomfort that comes \Nwith lying to her for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.67,0:20:09.79,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That'll be your atonement.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:17.17,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you still don't want to lie to her,\N then face her head on and don't run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:20.56,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll forgive you for running from your past.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.11,0:20:22.99,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.99,0:20:26.82,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At least don't run from the present or the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.82,0:20:29.96,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Did you just say something cool, Kadota?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.96,0:20:34.09,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That was awesome! I'm going to \Ncall you Poey the poet from now on...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.57,0:20:35.37,Secondary Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I just couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.67,0:20:38.46,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I tried. I went there numerous times...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.13,0:20:43.13,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,To simply tell her, "Let's break up."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:45.15,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.15,0:20:47.01,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I left the Yellow Scarves.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:49.76,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you already decided on a high school, Kida?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.98,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to take the exams for Raira Academy, since it's close.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.63,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept typing words in praise of Raira Academy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.26,0:20:57.94,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I was lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.37,0:21:00.52,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,When I talked to Mikado, I felt at ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.87,0:21:01.98,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,You should...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.98,0:21:02.69,Chat,,0000,0000,0000,,Come too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.69,0:21:05.69,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And so, I reunited with Mikado.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:07.41,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I also met Anri.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:11.47,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought that my peaceful life as a high schooler would continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.47,0:21:12.57,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,And yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.57,0:21:13.75,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.75,0:21:16.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You...You dragged me back into this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:18.21,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I had absolutely no intention of returning.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.54,0:21:21.32,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't run from her anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.32,0:21:26.29,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Your feelings of guilt towards her will become\N your past, and she'll become a deity to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.29,0:21:27.96,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,He was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.96,0:21:29.95,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.95,0:21:33.35,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat the Slasher, who hurt Anri and my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.88,0:21:36.86,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll defeat the Dollars if the Slasher's with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.86,0:21:38.87,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't freeze up any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.87,0:21:41.62,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,This time, I'll definitely...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.62,0:21:42.58,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.58,0:21:43.23,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.23,0:21:45.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl was spying on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.68,0:21:46.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone's chasing her as we speak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.98,0:21:48.08,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.08,0:21:49.98,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's with the Dollars!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:52.20,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to talk with her. Don't be too rough with her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.20,0:21:53.52,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.67,0:21:57.00,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go this way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.21,0:22:01.25,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't have been hesitant at all...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.66,0:22:04.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I returned. That's it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.94,0:22:06.51,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Yet, why...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:10.49,Thought,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is anxiety rippling throughout my body?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:21.01,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.56,0:22:22.34,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.52,0:22:24.90,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...is Kida...?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.35,0:24:02.12,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The girl runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.12,0:24:03.36,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,She runs as fast as she can...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.36,0:24:05.54,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,...to escape the shadow that's chasing her,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.04,0:24:09.92,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,to escape the horrible truth she's discovered.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.88,0:24:14.55,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Next Time: The Blue Dynasty is Dead.
